    "name": "HCL Healthcare API",
    "description": "API collection for HCL Healthcare Management System\n\nBase URL: https://hcl-healthcare-backend.onrender.com\n\nBefore testing:\n1. Import the collection\n2. Create an environment\n3. Set up environment variables:\n   - token\n   - userId\n   - shiftId",
